name: Flower
description: Symbolic flower in the colors of the Ukrainian flag.

name: Ukrainian Flag
description: Ukrainian national symbol. It symbolizes an endless field of wheat and a clear blue sky.

name: Tryzub
description: The Ukrainian coat of arms – trident, or tryzub – has a long history (over a thousand years, if not more), but at the same time, it is a symbol of a modern country. It is short-spoken – and meaningful as well. It reflects heroic events of the past – and it is a stripe of Ukrainian warriors protecting the sovereignty and territorial integrity of Ukraine today. The word Liberty is encrypted in the symbol.

name: Medicals
description: It will help to sew up a wound, treat an abrasion, purify water, save the life of oneself or a friend.

name: Nutrition
description: A complete well-balanced daily diet serving as a source of strength for the defenders of Ukraine.

name: Supply
description: As a result of the bombing of settlements, many people, in best case, were actually stayed without a livelihood. Therefore, tens of tons of humanitarian aid collecting for them every day.

name: Ambulance
description: The crew bravely continues to save lives, especially in wartime.

name: Mriya
description: The largest and most lifting aircraft in the history of world aviation in a single copy. Approximately 200 records were reached before it was substantially damaged.

name: Petrolium
description: Canister of fuel for supply vehicles, medical transport and infantry armored vehicles.

name: Helmet
description: Head armor, sniper protection, also it's easier to think wearing it.

name: Body Armour
description: Full set of chest armor. Protects against bullets, shrapnel and stray fragments.

name: Molotov
description: Glass bottle with Molotov cocktail. Folk remedy to fight the occupier. Effectively shows itself even against tanks.

name: Ukrainian Tank
description: Ukrainian modernization of the T72 tank with a more powerful engine, a new model cannon and a small anti-aircraft gun.

name: Javelin
description: Portable missile launcher. Launches homing guided missiles effective against ground armored vehicles and low-flying air targets.

name: Bayraktar
description: A small stealth drone armed with several guided bombs and missiles. Thunderstorm for infantry vehicles, tanks, fuel trucks.

name: Mig 29
description: Fighter aircraft, effective against a variety of air targets. This was piloted by the mythical  Ghost of Kyiv, who destroyed more than 20 aircraft.

name: Captured Tank
description: It is difficult to imagine the surprise of an enemy when a simple farmer on a simple tractor simply takes away his tank from under his nose.

name: Russian Warship
description: Rooskii voienniy korabl idi nakhuy — means “russian warship go fuck yourself“ — that was all the russian ship crew heard about their threats to ukrainian to lay down theirs arms and surrender.

name: Zelenskyi
description: Sixth President of Ukraine. He was destined to kick Putin's ass, which he successfully managed. Glory to Ukraine.

name: russian-nazzies
description: Unofficial prototype of the new small coat of arms of Ukraine. The symbol of the fight against Russian occupation.

name: Huilo
description: A cynical little evil man living in his own little world. He fancies himself the last defender of the spiritual bonds of the great Russian people. His propaganda has poisoned tens of millions of people in Russia. His army is attacking and storming Ukrainian cities for absolutely inconceivable reasons. Place him to the Jail.
